{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01UsBY2Qg5wdBJM2V5RHeTYS","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All the migrations have been completed successfully. Let me create a final summary of what was done:\n\n## Migration Summary: Quarkus to Spring Boot Messaging\n\nI have successfully migrated all the messaging classes from Quarkus SmallRye Reactive Messaging to Spring Boot's ApplicationEventPublisher pattern. Here's what was completed:\n\n### Files Modified:\n\n**1. MessageProducerService.java** \n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessageProducerService.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Removed `@ApplicationScoped` → Changed to `@Service`\n  - Removed `@Inject @Channel Emitter` → Changed to `@Autowired ApplicationEventPublisher`\n  - Updated all `brokerEmitter.send()` calls to `eventPublisher.publishEvent(new BrokerMessageEvent(...))`\n  - Updated all `streamerEmitter.send()` calls to `eventPublisher.publishEvent(new StreamerMessageEvent(...))`\n  - Removed imports: `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`, `jakarta.inject.Inject`, `org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.*`\n  - Added imports: `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`, `org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisher`, `org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n\n**2. DTBroker3MDB.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTBroker3MDB.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Removed `@ApplicationScoped` → Changed to `@Component`\n  - Removed `@Incoming(\"trade-broker-queue\")` → Changed to `@EventListener`\n  - Removed `@Transactional` (Jakarta) → Changed to `@Transactional` (Spring)\n  - Changed method signature from `onMessage(OrderMessage message)` to `onMessage(BrokerMessageEvent event)`\n  - Added `OrderMessage message = event.getMessage()` to extract the message from the event\n  - Removed imports: `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`, `jakarta.inject.Inject`, `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`, `org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.Incoming`\n  - Added imports: `org.springframework.context.event.EventListener`, `org.springframework.stereotype.Component`, `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`, `com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.messaging.BrokerMessageEvent`\n\n**3. DTStreamer3MDB.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTStreamer3MDB.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Removed `@ApplicationScoped` → Changed to `@Component`\n  - Removed `@Incoming(\"trade-streamer-topic\")` → Changed to `@EventListener`\n  - Changed method signature from `onMessage(QuoteUpdateMessage message)` to `onMessage(StreamerMessageEvent event)`\n  - Added `QuoteUpdateMessage message = event.getMessage()` to extract the message from the event\n  - Removed imports: `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`, `org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.Incoming`\n  - Added imports: `org.springframework.context.event.EventListener`, `org.springframework.stereotype.Component`, `com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.messaging.StreamerMessageEvent`\n\n### New Files Created:\n\n**4. BrokerMessageEvent.java** (NEW)\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/BrokerMessageEvent.java`\n- **Purpose**: Spring ApplicationEvent wrapper for OrderMessage\n- **Description**: This event replaces the Quarkus `@Channel(\"trade-broker-queue\")` in-memory channel\n\n**5. StreamerMessageEvent.java** (NEW)\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/StreamerMessageEvent.java`\n- **Purpose**: Spring ApplicationEvent wrapper for QuoteUpdateMessage\n- **Description**: This event replaces the Quarkus `@Channel(\"trade-streamer-topic\")` in-memory channel\n\n### Files Left Unchanged:\n\n**6. OrderMessage.java** - No changes needed (plain POJO with no Quarkus imports)\n\n**7. QuoteUpdateMessage.java** - No changes needed (plain POJO with no Quarkus imports)\n\n### Key Migration Points:\n\n1. **In-Memory Messaging**: Both Quarkus SmallRye Reactive Messaging and Spring Boot ApplicationEventPublisher provide in-memory event handling (no external broker)\n\n2. **Annotation Mapping**:\n   - Quarkus `@ApplicationScoped` → Spring `@Service` or `@Component`\n   - Quarkus `@Inject` → Spring `@Autowired`\n   - Quarkus `@Incoming` → Spring `@EventListener`\n   - Quarkus `@Channel + Emitter` → Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n   - Quarkus `@Transactional` (Jakarta) → Spring `@Transactional` (Spring)\n\n3. **Event Pattern**: Spring requires wrapping messages in ApplicationEvent subclasses, which is why we created BrokerMessageEvent and StreamerMessageEvent\n\n4. **Synchronous by Default**: Spring's ApplicationEventPublisher is synchronous by default. If async behavior is needed, you can add `@Async` to the `@EventListener` methods.\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated and are now using Spring Boot's native event system instead of Quarkus SmallRye Reactive Messaging!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"c6b4e0e9-760b-4063-b05b-c96e2e775436"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01YBYReZjaFW4KGk5xegMtep","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_017psnRQ9QskVahrAdDEatwb","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java","old_string":"// MIGRATION: javax.* -> jakarta.*\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.inject.Any;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.inject.Instance;\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\n\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.TradeServices;\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.TradeConfig;\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.TradeRunTimeModeLiteral;\n\n\n@Dependent\npublic class AsyncScheduledOrder implements Runnable {\n\n  TradeServices tradeService;\n\n  Integer orderID;\n  boolean twoPhase;\n\n  @Inject \n  public AsyncScheduledOrder(@Any Instance<TradeServices> services) {\n    tradeService = services.select(new TradeRunTimeModeLiteral(TradeConfig.getRunTimeModeNames()[TradeConfig.getRunTimeMode()])).get();\n  }","new_string":"// MIGRATION: Quarkus -> Spring Boot\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Scope;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.TradeServices;\n\n@Component\n@Scope(\"prototype\")\npublic class AsyncScheduledOrder implements Runnable {\n\n  TradeServices tradeService;\n\n  Integer orderID;\n  boolean twoPhase;\n\n  // MIGRATION: CDI Instance<TradeServices> with qualifiers -> Spring @Autowired with @Primary bean\n  @Autowired\n  public AsyncScheduledOrder(TradeServices tradeService) {\n    this.tradeService = tradeService;\n  }"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":494,"cache_read_input_tokens":71498,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":494,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":579},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Uc6kGPVjfMPcWC9DhiMNbo","session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"053968fa-5923-4311-b1e7-2a72947d4bcb"}
