{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01UZhsYDZNyNyQheiGkrHsVf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01BobEBTjxDJVPrp6hdz7gb1","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirect.java","old_string":"  // MIGRATION: JMS resources replaced with MessageProducerService\n  // Original Jakarta EE used JMS QueueConnectionFactory and TopicConnectionFactory\n  // Quarkus uses SmallRye Reactive Messaging via MessageProducerService\n\n  @Inject\n  private DataSource datasource;\n\n  @Inject\n  private UserTransaction txn;\n\n  @Inject\n  RecentQuotePriceChangeList recentQuotePriceChangeList;\n  \n  @Inject \n  AsyncOrderSubmitter asyncOrderSubmitter;  \n  \n  @Inject\n  @MarketSummaryUpdate\n  Event<String> mkSummaryUpdateEvent;\n  \n  // MIGRATION: ManagedExecutorService -> use CDI Event async\n  // For market summary updates, we use CDI Event.fireAsync()\n  \n  @Inject\n  MessageProducerService messageProducer;","new_string":"  // MIGRATION: JMS resources replaced with MessageProducerService\n  // Original Jakarta EE used JMS QueueConnectionFactory and TopicConnectionFactory\n  // Spring uses MessageProducerService for messaging\n\n  @Autowired\n  private DataSource datasource;\n\n  // MIGRATION: UserTransaction removed - using connection-level transaction management\n  // The TradeDirect class already manages transactions via Connection.commit()/rollback()\n\n  @Autowired\n  RecentQuotePriceChangeList recentQuotePriceChangeList;\n\n  @Autowired\n  AsyncOrderSubmitter asyncOrderSubmitter;\n\n  // MIGRATION: CDI Event<String> removed - not used in Spring\n  // Market summary updates handled by connection-level transactions\n\n  @Autowired\n  MessageProducerService messageProducer;"}}],"stop_reason":"tool