{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JYnW1zqvPsyZttBmVSsuri","type":"tool_result","content":"    60→ * interface\n    61→ *\n    62→ * Note: In order for this class to be thread-safe, a new TradeJDBC must be\n    63→ * created for each call to a method from the TradeInterface interface.\n    64→ * Otherwise, pooled connections may not be released.\n    65→ *\n    66→ * @see com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.TradeServices\n    67→ *\n    68→ */\n    69→\n    70→// MIGRATION: Quarkus @Dependent -> Spring @Component with @Scope(\"prototype\")\n    71→// MIGRATION: Custom @TradeJDBC qualifier -> Spring @Qualifier(\"tradeDirect\")\n    72→@Component(\"tradeDirect\")\n    73→@Scope(\"prototype\")\n    74→public class TradeDirect implements TradeServices, Serializable {\n    75→  /**\n    76→   * \n    77→   */\n    78→  private static final long serialVersionUID = -8089049090952927985L;\n    79→\n    80→  //This lock is used to serialize market summary operations.\n    81→  private static final Integer marketSummaryLock = new Integer(0);\n    82→  private static long nextMarketSummary = System.currentTimeMillis();\n    83→  private static MarketSummaryDataBean cachedMSDB = MarketSummaryDataBean.getRandomInstance();\n    84→\n    85→  private static BigDecimal ZERO = new BigDecimal(0.0);\n    86→  private boolean inGlobalTxn = false;\n    87→  private boolean inSession = false;\n    88→\n    89→  // MIGRATION: JMS resources replaced with MessageProducerService\n    90→  // Original Jakarta EE used JMS QueueConnectionFactory and TopicConnectionFactory\n    91→  // Spring uses MessageProducerService for messaging\n    92→\n    93→  @Autowired\n    94→  private DataSource datasource;\n    95→\n    96→  // MIGRATION: UserTransaction removed - using connection-level transaction management\n    97→  // The TradeDirect class already manages transactions via Connection.commit()/rollback()\n    98→\n    99→  @Autowired\n\n<system-reminde