{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01CxhQtTFdoeX2HdD3ibtBM3","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→#!/usr/bin/env python3\n     2→\"\"\"\n     3→Smoke tests for DayTrader Spring Boot application.\n     4→Tests core REST API endpoints to verify the migration works correctly.\n     5→\"\"\"\n     6→\n     7→import json\n     8→import os\n     9→import sys\n    10→import time\n    11→import urllib.request\n    12→import urllib.error\n    13→import urllib.parse\n    14→\n    15→BASE_URL = os.environ.get(\"APP_URL\", \"http://localhost:8080\")\n    16→REST_BASE = f\"{BASE_URL}/rest\"\n    17→\n    18→passed = 0\n    19→failed = 0\n    20→errors = []\n    21→\n    22→\n    23→def test(name, fn):\n    24→    global passed, failed, errors\n    25→    try:\n    26→        fn()\n    27→        passed += 1\n    28→        print(f\"  PASS: {name}\")\n    29→    except Exception as e:\n    30→        failed += 1\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"853ba17b-36cf-4cbe-9ea2-bc66a7e3b7f1"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_017Wp2pPYHd7ds2n14uvYWr3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The problem is that `spring.mvc.servlet.path=/rest` puts the Spring MVC DispatcherServlet at `/rest/*` but the Actuator endpoints are at the root context. However, the actuator might not be accessible. Let me update application.properties to put actuator at a known path and fix the smoke test:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":853,"cache_read_input_tokens":149160,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":853,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":183},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"28ca869f-01a4-412f-b877-5e1d61f8a2c6"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_017Wp2pPYHd7ds2n14uvYWr3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_018i8w1sRwiRSKq9Lh9HGqiV","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/resources/application.properties"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":853,"cache_read_input_tokens":149160,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":853,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":183},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"38c49e5f-7267-41d8-b05f-e9331e030723"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_018i8w1sRwiRSKq9Lh9HGqiV","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Spring Boot Application Configuration\n     2→spring.application.name=daytrader\n     3→\n     4→# HTTP port\n     5→server.port=8080\n     6→server.servlet.context-path=/\n     7→\n     8→# ===========================================\n     9→# Database Configuration\n    10→# ===========================================\n    11→spring.datasource.url=jdbc:h2:mem:tradedb;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1\n    12→spring.datasource.username=sa\n    13→spring.datasource.password=\n    14→spring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.h2.Driver\n    15→\n    16→# JPA/Hibernate\n    17→spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop\n    18→spring.jpa.show-sql=false\n    19→spring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect\n    20→spring.jpa.open-in-view=true\n    21→\n    22→# ===========================================\n    23→# REST Configuration\n    24→# ===========================================\n    25→# Spring MVC base path for REST controllers\n    26→spring.mvc.servlet.path=/rest\n    27→\n    28→# ===========================================\n    29→# Trade Application Configuration\n    30→# ===========================================\n    31→trade.runtime-mode=EJB3\n    32→trade.order-processing-mode=SYNCH\n    33→trade.max-users=50\n    34→trade.max-quotes=100\n    35→\n    36→# Database population on startup\n    37→trade.db.populate.on.startup=true\n    38→\n    39→# ===========================================\n    40→# Actuator (Health checks)\n    41→# ===========================================\n    42→management.endpoints.web.exposure.include=health,info\n    43→management.endpoint.health.show-details=always\n    44→\n    45→# ===========================================\n    46→# Jackson Configuration\n    47→# ===========================================\n    48→spring.jackson.serialization.fail-on-empty-beans=false\n    49→spring.jackson.serialization.write-dates-as-timestamps=true\n    50→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"7205f59d-9295-4a00-afa2-dbea3a79e93e"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01LqNtTAX7cTUZeR3mP27CAo","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is that `spring.mvc.servlet.path=/rest` puts the DispatcherServlet at `/rest` but the actuator uses a separate `management.server.base-path`. With `spring.mvc.servlet.path=/rest`, the actuator endpoints are served by a different servlet and they're at `/actuator/health` by default. But I got a 404. Let me check if it's because the actuator endpoints are also routed through the DispatcherServlet:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":812,"cache_read_input_tokens":150013,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":812,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":217},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"61ac09d8-72be-4ac2-8479-6ebd56db3ebf"}
