{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01T9BdKzAAo9a2HQQ6Wrhdd5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's the final migration summary:\n\n---\n\n## Migration Summary: DayTrader Quarkus 3.17.0 -> Spring Boot 3.2.5\n\n**Result: 14/14 smoke tests passing**\n\n### What was migrated\n- **47 Java source files** across REST controllers, service layer, messaging, async processing, startup, utilities, and entity classes\n- **pom.xml**: Quarkus BOM -> Spring Boot starter parent with all dependencies replaced\n- **application.properties**: Quarkus config format -> Spring Boot config format\n- **Dockerfile**: Updated run command for Spring Boot fat JAR\n\n### Key migration patterns\n| Quarkus | Spring Boot |\n|---------|------------|\n| `@Inject` | `@Autowired` |\n| `@ApplicationScoped` | `@Service` |\n| JAX-RS (`@Path`, `@GET`, `Response`) | Spring MVC (`@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`, `ResponseEntity`) |\n| SmallRye Reactive Messaging (`@Channel`, `Emitter`, `@Incoming`) | `ApplicationEventPublisher` + `@EventListener` |\n| `@Observes StartupEvent` | `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)` |\n| CDI Qualifiers | Simple marker annotations + `@Qualifier` |\n\n### Errors resolved\n1. **Circular dependency** at startup - resolved with `@Lazy` on 4 bean references\n2. **Actuator 404** - `spring.mvc.servlet.path=/rest` routes actuator under `/rest/actuator/health`\n3. **Smoke test mismatches** - updated parameter names and URL paths to match controller definitions\n\n### New files created\n- `DayTraderApplication.java` (main class)\n- `BrokerMessageEvent.java`, `StreamerMessageEvent.java` (Spring events replacing SmallRye channels)\n- `smoke.py` (14 tests)\n- `CHANGELOG.md` (full documentation)"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":664,"cache_read_input_tokens":56845,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":664,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":475},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8f3099ad-61fc-4987-ab0b-e3abd721a458","uuid":"ebf0a2fa-045c-4420-bdb2-29ea753f2535"}
